name: IS IT THE END OF R.O.B's LIFE?
description:
R.O.B and the gang are in big trouble. While they visited John Karel's window, a legendary space giant monster, 'Elprup XIII' invaded the place. Will they be survive? or is it the end of R.O.B's life?

My tribute to John Karel's iconic Window Collection! @jjjjjjjjjjohn
